258
00:14:10,993 --> 00:14:13,823
<b>You showing up and bossing me around like this...</b>

259
00:14:14,693 --> 00:14:16,193
<b>exhausts me.</b>

260
00:14:18,162 --> 00:14:19,762
<b>You should go back to Seoul now.</b>

261
00:14:26,802 --> 00:14:29,573
