277
00:15:37,613 --> 00:15:39,142
<b>Yes, exactly.</b>

278
00:15:39,743 --> 00:15:41,042
<b>We should...</b>

279
00:15:41,613 --> 00:15:44,483
<b>close down the ice skating rink.</b>

280
00:15:44,713 --> 00:15:46,422
