283
00:15:52,623 --> 00:15:56,062
<b>All right, enjoy.</b>

284
00:16:01,463 --> 00:16:04,032
<b>Oh, okay. Sure.</b>

285
00:16:04,032 --> 00:16:06,772
<b>Hello! Yes.</b>

286
00:16:08,103 --> 00:16:11,113
